  "description": "Rule 90 — the Sierpinski triangle woven across eight arms. Inherently fractal, inherently ordered. mutationRate at 0.01 means the pattern barely shifts: the octopus has found its configuration and is content to hold it. armSpread at 0.3 keeps the voices close, not scattered. Chaos at 0.05 — just a breath of unpredictability. Long attack and release. The cellular automata at peace, its pattern a lullaby of recursion.",
